data.description: Welcome to your dream residence in heart of prestigious Riverwalk Subdivision. A gorgeous brick, tree lined neighborhood entry sets the tone for luxury living. Enjoy  access to a private neighborhood boat launch, perfect for those who love waterside adventures.  When you are not out on the water, relax by your very own inground swimming pool, a true oasis for summertime fun. As you enter the home, you're greeted by a cozy fireplace, creating a warm ambiance.  This  home offers a blend of functionality and elegance. There's dedicated office space for professional work or remote tasks.  The kitchen boasts of granite countertops, brick flooring and  stainless steel appliances.  It's well equipped for hosting corporate gatherings or family dinners. The walk in closets offer generous storage space for clothing and personal items.  The laundry room has utility sink and spacious closet.  This spacious residence features 4 bedroom 2 and 1 half baths providing ample room for family or guests..  The split plan design ensures privacy and comfort. Enjoy morning coffee or evening cocktails from your front or back porch. This corner lot beams with beautiful oaks, landscaping and has a side entry double garage.  This property is just north of Promenade Shopping for easy, quick access to shopping and dining. Call for your showing today! Seller will give your choice of $5,000 reduction from sales price or $5,000 credit at closing to replace the pool liner.
